title: STÜSSY Unveils Its Women's SS17 Lookbook
text:
Previous Next 
As New York Fashion Week get underway, streetwear brand Stüssy unveiled its new Spring/Summer 2017 women’s lookbook. 
The collection features relaxed and loose fitting silhouettes with bold, standout hues that evoke images of Nineties skatewear. Featuring sweaters, long-sleeved polo shirts and bomber jackets, the collection is more than likely to be a hit among Stüssy fans this summer. 
Stüssy also recently unveiled the men’s lookbook for SS17, which sees the collection feature American sportswear classics and relaxed silhouettes. Also be sure to check out the California brand’s incredible new Spring campaign here . 
In other fashion news, Palace teases its new Spring 2017 collection.
